  <!-- EN: poorly organized trading fair -->
  <VME_PoorlyOrganizedTradingFair.stages.poorly_organized_trading_fair.label>组织糟糕的贸易展会</VME_PoorlyOrganizedTradingFair.stages.poorly_organized_trading_fair.label>
  <!-- EN: With such a low quality effort, no additional caravans will be attracted to our settlement... -->
